#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can draw curves by using this tool. Click |mouseleft| to indicate the starting point of the curve, then click again for consecutive control points of the curve. While creating a control point, "
"drag to create the handles, they will show as red lines."
msgstr "このツールでは曲線を描くことができます。曲線の始点を |mouseleft| クリックで示し、再度クリックして操作点を作成します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:23
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With an intermediate control point (i.e. a point that is not the starting point and not the ending point), you can move the direction handles separately to have the curve enter and leave the point "
"in different directions. After editing a point, you can just click on the canvas to continue adding points to the curve. When creating a path on a vector layer, the resulting path can be further "
"edited with the :ref:`shape_edit_tool`."
msgstr "ベクターレイヤーでは、前追加された操作点をクリックして編集することができます。中間操作点(例えば開始や終了地点でない点)で、その点に入って出ていく向きを異なる方向にすることができます。編集した後は、キャンバス上をクリックすれば曲線への点の追加を続行できます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:27
msgid ".. image:: /images/tools/path_tool_usage.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:27
msgid ""
"The path preview that shows while drawing a path. The start of the path is indicated with a white square, the preview for the path itself in black, and the red dotted lines being the control points "
"for the current handle."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:29
msgid "Double-click |mouseleft| on any point of the curve or press the :kbd:`Enter` key to finish drawing, or press the :kbd:`Esc` key to cancel the entire curve."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/path.rst:31
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While drawing a curve, pressing the :kbd:`Ctrl` key while dragging will push the handles both ways. The :kbd:`Alt` key will create a sharp corner, and the :kbd:`Shift` key will allow you to make a "
"handle while at the end of the curve. |mouseright| will undo the last added point."
msgstr "ドラッグしつつ :kbd:`Ctrl` キーを押して描くことでハンドルを両方の方向に出すことができます。:kbd:`Alt` キーで角ばった角にすることができ、:kbd:`Shift` キーで曲線の終わりでもハンドルを作ることができます。|mouseright| で最後に追加された点を取り消します。"

